snippet.textDisplay:
Umair Jaswal nailed this song a hundred times over and lifted the entire passion of this song with his unhindered dance. This man exudes confidence, doesnt give a flying rats ass to what you think, enjoys his music and sings it with the perfection of a soulful singer with a grounding in rock music. I understand that there are many who may not like his body language throughout - because its different. But I truly believe his is the body language everyone performing such an uplifting song should have. 

A classy and mermerising rendition by both Umair Jaswal and QB. Love, from Bangladesh.
